  "description": "The Circuit Breakers are back! Dive into the fast, chaotic twin-stick shooter built for pure arcade action. Battle through swarms of robots solo or with up to 6 players in local or online co-op, rack up high scores, unlock achievements, and bring your progress anywhere with cloud saves.\n\nSUPER CIRCUIT BREAKERS delivers classic pick-up-and-play action with modern upgrades, including expanded display support, Steam Deck compatibility, Steam Input, and improved performance. Whether you're chasing leaderboard-worthy runs, teaming up with friends, or just looking to blow up thousands of bots, there’s never been a better time to break some circuits.\n\nJump into the action:\n\n• Up to 6-player local and online multiplayer\n\n• Cloud saves across your devices\n\n• Steam Workshop character skins\n\n• 4 free characters, plus a free weekly character rotation\n\n• Like seriously, this is one of 10 games on Steam that supports 6 players\n\n• Fully supported Controller, Mouse, or Mouse + Keyboard controls\n\n• A jammin' soundtrack\n\n• Free updates with extra content\n\n• A perfectly mesmerizing Attract Mode\n\n• Steam Deck mode, Steam Input support, and ultrawide compatibility",
  "description_short": "Back with new weapons, new enemies, and with more circuits to break than ever! Destroy millions of robots in this free-to-play shooter with up to 6 players local or online.",
